cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.MM 

This paper deals with facial expression recognition using deep learning models, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the challenges of recognizing human emotions, which can be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses a large image database (AffectNet), which can be related to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
